OL,3,C'Major incident' as fire breaks out at
OL,4,Crecycling centre
OL,6,FA large fire which broke out at a
OL,7,Frecycling centre in Avonmouth has now
OL,8,Fbeen declared a "major incident".
OL,10,FAvon Fire and Rescue were called to
OL,11,Fthe scene on Kings Weston Lane shortly
OL,12,Fafter 1:30am on Wednesday 15 July.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the fire service said:
OL,15,F"All personnel at the site were safely
OL,16,Fevacuated and there are currently no
OL,17,Freported casualties.
OL,19,F"Avon and Somerset Police are also in
OL,20,Fattendance and are supporting with
OL,21,Froad closures."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
