OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784184477
OL,3,C'Major incident' as fire breaks out at
OL,4,Crecycling centre
OL,6,FCrews from 14 stations including
OL,7,FAvonmouth, Bedminster and Weston-super-
OL,8,FMare attended the incident, supported
OL,9,Fby specialist resources, including
OL,10,Fturntable ladders and high-volume
OL,11,Fpumps.
OL,13,FFirefighters are continuing to work to
OL,14,Fbring the flames under control and
OL,15,Femergency services remain in
OL,16,Fattendance.
OL,18,FPeople living in the area are being
OL,19,Fasked to keep doors and windows closed
OL,20,Fand to stay indoors where possible.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
