OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784184477
OL,3,C'Major incident' as fire breaks out at
OL,4,Crecycling centre
OL,6,FKings Weston Lane is closed between
OL,7,Fthe A403 St Andrews Road and Long
OL,8,FCross while the fire crews work on
OL,9,Fcontrolling the blaze.
OL,11,FThe public is also being asked to
OL,12,Favoid the area and to expect
OL,13,Fdisruption while emergency services
OL,14,Fcontinue their response.
